oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Panorama photograph of 26th MG Battn.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: This panorama photograph of the 26th MG Battn. shows the unit in an outdoor setting with many trees in the background. The officers and NCOs are seated in the front row with the rest of the men standing on four rows of risers behind Pvt. Andrew Sherrill is 4th from the right in the back row.
